    "description": {
      "value": "<p>From birth you have a monkey-like tail of any color you wish. </p><p>At 1st level, your tail is strong enough to hold small objects such as lanterns or Kunai, keeping your hands free. You may use a bonus action to make a ranged weapon attack with a weapon with the thrown and light property.</p><p>Beginning at the 11th level you can make 2 attacks.</p>",
